thread.title: BRIEF-Oncology Venture Announces Positive Interim Results From A Phase 1/2 Study

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Oncology Venture Announces Positive Interim Results From A Phase 1/2 Study
text:
Jan 31 (Reuters) - ONCOLOGY VENTURE SWEDEN AB:
* ANNOUNCES POSITIVE INTERIM RESULTS FROM A PHASE 1/2 STUDY WITH LIPLACIS AND ITS DRP IN HEAVILY PRETREATED METASTATIC BREAST CANCER PATIENTS
* STUDY IS PROGRESSING ACCORDING TO PLAN, AND LAST PATIENT IS EXPECTED TO BE INCLUDED BEFORE END OF Q1 2018.
* ‍LAST PATIENT IS EXPECTED TO BE INCLUDED BEFORE END OF Q1 2018.​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom)
